                  <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh] animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 duration-700">
                    <div className="max-w-xl w-full">
                       <div className="text-center mb-10">
                          <h2 className="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tight mb-4">为您推荐那一碗香喷喷的米饭</h2>
                          <p className="text-gray-400 text-lg font-medium">采用多模态特征融合技术，为您精准画像</p>
